{"tid":536630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最賤格和最多大話的女人","createTime":"2018-01-22T03:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T03:38:42.000Z","uid":54499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b03efab41a0ecb3643926ea6c365d695477147","tid":536630,"uid":54499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"轉載自我朋友既FB<br />\n<br />\n扮可憐打電話叫我放過佢，自己有男朋友，同我個朋友上床，𠱓我個朋友話有咗佢個BB🤰叫我朋友比100萬佢💰～跟住仲要講大話，恐嚇我🙈🙈🙈～我有晒全部WhatsApp訊息證據！😒😒😒明明老豆係執垃圾嘅，窮等人家，屋企住幾千蚊租冇廚房嘅單位，其實佢講真話無人會睇唔起佢，竟然同我講話自己係中山有房地產公司，買咗幾層樓收租，講到自己好有錢咁，😍😍😍仲叫我如果有錢嘅幫我轉錢去柬埔寨，話而家柬埔寨啲樓價平，我去嗰度買層樓做乜嘢啊？餵蚊？唔知以為洗黑錢的🤔🤔🤔，我問佢攞公司卡片，竟然連一張卡片都冇，冇卡片唔緊要，我問佢攞公司網站，又冇，咁我之後咪問佢攞公司地址囉，都係冇😂😂🤣🤦&zwj;♀️～低級騙子！最重要嘅係識佢嘅人都覺得佢係一個好有機心，好有部署，好勢利，好貪錢，同埋好古靈精怪嘅女人！可惜佢將佢嘅聰明用咗係錯誤嘅地方！<br />\n<br />\n上年9月24號同我講話有咗BB依家都1月啦，有冇人見到佢個肚？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/113202_6a4b3a8d370a369fa823ddd4ec86da1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F113202_6a4b3a8d370a369fa823ddd4ec86da1e.jpg&h=45422866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/113210_809f16cff4bc06bc7b6f02b425edf322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F113210_809f16cff4bc06bc7b6f02b425edf322.jpg&h=a45cb4ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/113220_45bf4142a45bd38100e50e9919194611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F113220_45bf4142a45bd38100e50e9919194611.jpg&h=af0bb5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/113223_2e59f26c1386a444f966af507db9e059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F113223_2e59f26c1386a444f966af507db9e059.jpg&h=de6ab389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservic